To start scss live reloader:
  navigate to the css style folder
  sass .scss .css
  sass --watch style.scss

To start DT's hipstarter platform:

  1. clone into your own folder
  git clone https://github.com/epoch/hipstarter.git new_foldername
    template command: $ git clone url new_folder_name

  2. cd into new folder and install dependencies

  3. $ npm install
  4.  start developing
      $ npm start
  5. run page in browser
  navigate to localhost:3000 or change port in gulpfile
